Slide â€” DR Environment Implementation Summary

We have successfully built a complete Azure-based Disaster Recovery environment with the following components:

Network Setup: VNet, Subnets, IP Prefix, Public IPs

Secure Connectivity: IPSec Tunnel, VPN Gateways, Firewall/WAF, NSGs, Bastion Host

Compute & Storage: SQL Server VM, Storage Accounts, Containers, Golden Images

DNS & Identity: Full DNS replica of on-prem zones and records in DR

Replication & Recovery: Azure Site Recovery (ASR) with policies, replication, and recovery plans

Automation: Majority of deployment done using Terraform, Bash, Azure CLI integrated with Automation Accounts

Outcome: A secure, scalable, and automated DR environment ready for failover with consistent network, compute, and DNS configuration matching on-prem infrastructure.



